%h2 Publish Tree

%p
  Publishing the tree affects all of the following pages. All drafts and reviews will become live. Are you sure you want to proceed?

%table.index#page-picker
  %col{:width => "70%"}
  %col{:width => "30%"}
  %thead
    %tr
      %th Page
      %th Status
  %tbody
    = render :partial => "admin/page/dp_node", :object => @homepage, :locals => {:level => 0}

- form_tag do
  %p.buttons
    = hidden_field_tag :root, params[:root]
    = submit_tag "Publish Tree", :name => "publish", :class => "button", :style => "margin-left: 2em;"
    or
    = link_to 'Cancel', page_index_url(:root => params[:root])